and aspire to be as good as?

00:36:32.250 --> 00:36:34.590
KEVIN BLAKE: So one
magician I admire and aspire

00:36:34.590 --> 00:36:41.080
to be as good as,
hopefully, is right here.

00:36:41.080 --> 00:36:43.144
David Gerard-- everyone,
David Gerard right here.

00:36:43.144 --> 00:36:44.435
Google magician extraordinaire.

00:36:44.435 --> 00:36:47.286
DAVID GERARD: I have a badge.

00:36:47.286 --> 00:36:49.260
KEVIN BLAKE: David's
